text: Vannes is a commune. It is the prefecture of Morbihan in Brittany. == Education == * Institut catholique d'arts et métiers ==Sister cities== Vannes is twinned with: * Mons, Belgium (since 1952) * Cuxhaven, Germany (since 1963) * Fareham, United Kingdom (since 1967) Vannes also has partnerships (‘partenariats’) with: * Barouéli, Mali, since 2003 * Wałbrzych, Poland, since 2001
title: Vannes
